title: Parasite 2
overview: When Tootsie meets Mark, a well-known street figure, sparks fly. However, Tootsie's schemes land her in hot water when she falls for a vengeful figure, Lucas, who has a hidden agenda against Mark. Torn between her parasitic habits and genuine affection, Tootsie must make a harrowing choice as her manipulative tendencies bring her face-to-face with the consequences of her actions.
